<p>The Aastra 312w is suitable for small, medium and large enterprises and all vertical sectors that require a mobile work force.</p>
<p>The Aastra 312w provides the best of Voice over WLAN with 
user-friendly interface, a high resolution colour display and state of 
the art security. It also offers all the features appreciated by 
demanding users: hands-free operation, headset connector and a vibrating
 alert.</p>
<p>The Aastra 312 can be easily deployed and managed from very small to 
extremely large installations. The telephone supports SIP and is thus 
compatible with most open-standard IP environments. It has also been 
successfully tested with a large number of wireless access points to 
broaden its appeal.</p>
<p>A Memory-Card saves up to 100 phonebook entries, device-specific data
 and the MAC-address. When replacing the handset, a new registration is 
not necessary if the MEM-Card is transferred to the new device. </p><div style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://pages.ebay.nl/selling_manager_pro"><img border="0" height="50" width="248" src="http://pics.ebay.com/aw/pics/nl/sellingmanager/sellingmanagerPro/smPro_248x50.gif"></a></div>')
